Ernest Van Pelt https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ernest_Van_Pelt 0 Ernest Van Pelt (31 March 1883 – 1 July 1961) was an American actor. Ernest Van Pelt was born on 31 March 1883 in Kansas.Van Pelt was a regular player in the films of Charlie Chaplin and others. Van Pelt died on 1 July 1961.
